                     <msItem xml:id="p1_i1">
                        <locus from="1ra" to="3vb"/>
                        <title type="incomplete"/>
                        <!--ref="LIT2736RepCh20"-->
                        <!--new work authority file-->
                        <note>Two or more lines were cut off, possibly when all edges were trimmed
                           (<!--see under condition-->). It is also possible that the binder who
                           incorporated <locus from="1" to="3"/> into the codex, cut of a part of
                           the bottom margin in order to adjust the size of the folia to the size of
                           the text block. The ink is partly rubbed off , single characters are
                           therefore not legible.</note>
                        <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        <note> The hymnodic portrait poem praises the Trinity and comprises at least
                           50 strophes. It is an unknown (?) version of the <foreign xml:lang="gez"
                              >Malkǝʾa Śǝllāse</foreign>. It clearly differs from the known version
                              <ref type="work" corresp="LIT2736RepCh20"/> witnessed in many
                           manuscripts and in printed editions, e.g. <bibl><ptr
                                 target="bm:1955Malkǝʿa Gubāʾe"/></bibl>.</note>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                           <locus target="#1ra"/>
                           <pb n="1r"/>
                           <cb n="a"/>
                           <hi rend="rubric">ሰላም፡ ለሕላዌክሙ፡ ዘኢርትዓ፡</hi> ዓወቅ፡ ጥንቱ፡ ወኢይትዓመር፡ ትፍጻሜቱ፡
                           አጋእዝትየ፡ <hi rend="rubric">ሥላሴ፡</hi> ዘኢትመውቱ፡ እንዘ፡ ፫፩ወእንዘ፡ ፩፫ቱ፡ ዕበይክሙ፡
                           ትፍጻሜ፡ አልቦቱ። <hi rend="rubric">ሰላ፡</hi> ለዝክረ፡ ስምክሙ፡ ዘይጥዕም፡ እምሀሊብ። ወእምነ፡
                           መዓር፡ ፃማ፡ እደ፡ ገብሩ፡ ለንህብ። </incipit>
                        <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                           <locus target="#3vb"/><hi rend="rubric">ሰ፡</hi> ለቆምክሙ፡ አጋእዝትየ፡ ሥላሴ፡ ዳ<gap
                              reason="illegible" unit="chars" extent="2"/><!-- ነቢይ፡ እንዘ፡ ይብል፡ ሃሌ፡ ይቤሎ፡
                           እግዚ፡ ለእግዚእየ፡ ንበር፡ በየማንየ፡ ወልድ፡ ሂል፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ካዕበ፡ አሪ?አየ። ዕ?ክሙ፡ አጋእዝትየ፡
                           <hi rend="rubric">ሥ፡</hi> በከመ፡ ሙሴ?፡ በውስተ፡ ኦሪት፡ እንዘ፡ ይብል፡ ተር ብሔር፡ እግዚእ፡ እምቅድመ፡-->
